hymns.content:
Ekidd: 
Azuukidde, tali muno
Yezu Kabaka agenze nno, tali muno!
E Galilaya gye mulimusanga,
E Galilaya gye mulimusanga.

1. Abakedde eyo gy’ebaamuziika
Basanzeyo Malayika n’abagamba;
//‘‘Takyaali mu ntaana Yezu Kabaka,
Takyaali mu ntaana.’’//

2. Mwe eddembe eryange libaddeko mmwe
Eddembe eryange lye lya Kitange!
//‘Nzuuno ddala mulabe abaana,
Sikyali mu ntaana.’//

3. Abaana be abatume aboolesa ebyo
Mu mbiriizi n’ebibatu nalaga ebyo;
//Bakakasa mazima Yezu Kabaka
Wuuno ddala omuzira//

4. Atwagala Yezu Kabaka abaana be ffe
Awaddeyo obulamu olw’okuba ffe;
//Ggwe Musumba omuzira olwanye,
Ssebo tusiimye nnyo//

5. Luwangula omugabe ow’ekitiibwa,
Olwanye nnyo olutalo n’ogoba olwo
//Ssemigero omuzira olwanye,
Ggwe muzira asinga//.

6. Otuggyeko ekinene eky’akabi ffe
Ffe abaana bo tufuge tuli naawe
//Naffe tuli mu liryo eggye eryo
Tuwondera Omuzira//.
